name: CPUTimes
summary: Simple object holding the data for a logical cpu execution times.

properties.name: idle
properties.summary: The number of milliseconds the CPU has spent in idle mode.

properties.name: irq
properties.summary: The number of milliseconds the CPU has spent in irq mode.

properties.name: nice
properties.summary: The number of milliseconds the CPU has spent in nice mode.

properties.name: sys
properties.summary: The number of milliseconds the CPU has spent in sys mode.

properties.name: user
properties.summary: The number of milliseconds the CPU has spent in user mode.
